@startuml
actor User as User
participant "Conversation Service" as Conv
participant "Conversation DB" as ConvDB
participant "RabbitMQ Broker" as RabbitMQ
participant "Chatbot Service" as Chatbot
participant "Chatbot DB" as ChatbotDB
participant "R2 Object Storage" as R2

== Luồng Thu hồi chia sẻ cuộc trò chuyện ==
User -> Conv: DELETE /code-conversation-service/shared-chats/:shareId
activate Conv

Conv -> ConvDB: UPDATE Share (isActive=false) & INSERT Outbox (ShareRevokedEvent)
activate ConvDB
ConvDB --> Conv: Commit Transaction (Atomic)
deactivate ConvDB

Conv --> User: HTTP 200 OK (Xác nhận thu hồi thành công)
deactivate Conv

== Relayer quét Outbox gửi đi ==
note over Conv, RabbitMQ: Cron job OutboxRelay quét DB định kỳ gửi event
Conv -> ConvDB: SELECT PENDING OutboxEvents
activate ConvDB
ConvDB --> Conv: Danh sách events
deactivate ConvDB

Conv -> RabbitMQ: Publish 'ShareRevokedEvent' (Queue: share_revoked)
activate RabbitMQ
RabbitMQ --> Conv: Ack
deactivate RabbitMQ

Conv -> ConvDB: UPDATE Outbox status='DONE'
activate ConvDB
ConvDB --> Conv: OK
deactivate ConvDB

== Chatbot xử lý thu hồi ==
RabbitMQ --> Chatbot: Consume 'ShareRevokedEvent'
activate Chatbot

Chatbot -> R2: Yêu cầu xóa file JSONL khỏi R2 (delete_file)
activate R2
R2 --> Chatbot: OK (Đã xóa file)
deactivate R2

Chatbot -> ChatbotDB: UPDATE Share (is_revoked=True, version=version)
activate ChatbotDB
ChatbotDB --> Chatbot: OK
deactivate ChatbotDB

Chatbot --> RabbitMQ: Acknowledge (Hoàn thành)
deactivate Chatbot
@enduml
